WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.460
Misato-chan didn’t show up at school again today, so I took my notes to her home.

00:04.890 --> 00:08.990
Misato-chan’s mom came to the door, but Misato-chan didn’t.

00:09.580 --> 00:11.720
Is she feeling so bad that she can’t even come to the door?

00:12.260 --> 00:15.550
Could it be that she doesn’t like me anymore?

00:16.120 --> 00:17.730
That would make me very sad.

00:18.340 --> 00:22.270
No matter what other kids say about Misato-chan, I’ll always be her friend.

00:22.730 --> 00:24.410
I want to see you, Misato-chan.
